snippet.title: Tea Garden Simulator 1.0 is available NOW!
snippet.description:
Tea Garden Simulator leaves early access, and the full game is available now to play on PC (Steam)! 
Get the game 👉 https://www.teagardensimulator.com/
Discord 👉 https://discord.gg/6DjHkTm
Twitter 👉 @TeaGardenSim

Tea Garden Simulator is a farming simulation game that's almost limitless in terms of what you can achieve with tea. Our tea chemistry sim engine can simulate every stage of the tea-making process. Using science, you may discover the mysteries of tea making and experiment with new ideas. 🌿

👉 Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1401340/Tea_Garden_Simulator/
